      "type": "document",
      "name": "OpenTAP 9.29 发布说明",
      "filePath": "doc/Release Notes/9.29/Readme.md",
      "summary": "OpenTAP 9.29.0 版本发布说明，涵盖从 .NET Framework 迁移到 .NET 9 的重大变更、多语言支持功能、增强的 Mixin 功能，以及若干新特性和 Bug 修复。",
      "tags": [
        "release-notes",
        "documentation",
        "changelog"
      ],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "document:doc/Release Notes/9.30/Readme.md",
      "type": "document",
      "name": "OpenTAP 9.30 发布说明",
      "filePath": "doc/Release Notes/9.30/Readme.md",
      "summary": "OpenTAP 9.30.0 版本发布说明，主要包含 API 增强（自定义名称格式化接口 IFormatName、DisplayAttribute 中性语言变体）以及测试步骤断开条件导致死锁的 Bug 修复。",
      "tags": [
        "release-notes",
        "documentation",
        "changelog"
      ],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
